{"tid":884894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳智庫：解放軍10年派2500人隱瞞與軍方關係，與外國大學合作獲軍事科技","createTime":"2018-11-01T03:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T03:07:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9a61f6af644cecdec8eb9bcd3cd54155ee8babb8","tid":884894,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20181101/s00013/1541010446723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181101%2Fs00013%2F1541010446723&d=b7DOn9OyI3Miq2JAdG7N8Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e046fee9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181101%2Fs00013%2F1541010446723&h=12094f2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20181101/s00013/1541010446723</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】澳洲戰略政策研究所（Australian Strategic Policy Institute）周二發布的一份報告稱，中國軍方正在擴大與外國大學的合作，而且有時會隱瞞其科學家與軍方的聯繫。這份報告提到：那些對中國崛起持謹慎態度的國家，是否其實在為中國的軍事進步做直接的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n10年派2500人 隱瞞與軍方關係<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》引述該份報告稱，解放軍在過去的10年裏，把2500名軍方科學家、研究人員和工程師派往海外。這些人與世界各地的學者和科學家合作，尤其集中在美國、英國、澳洲、新西蘭和加拿大，也就是廣泛共享情報的所謂「五眼」（Five Eyes）國家。報告還稱，中國和西方科學家聯合發表的同行評議論文數量在同一時期增長了7倍多，從2007年的95篇增加到去年的734篇。<br />\n<br />\n這些合作研究有時是在具有戰略軍事應用的領域，如導航技術、量子物理和密碼學。"},{"pid":"c3ee116323f33ffc8fa603b357010ce4ddd0c149","tid":884894,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/china-spy-recruitment-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fchina-spy-recruitment-us%2F&d=b7DOn9OyI3Miq2JAdG7N8Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=96a29fa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wired.com/story/china-spy-recruitment-us/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/us-china-cybertheft-su-bin/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fus-china-cybertheft-su-bin%2F&d=b7DOn9OyI3Miq2JAdG7N8Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e9ced7c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wired.com/story/us-china-cybertheft-su-bin/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢兩篇報導好詳細。基本上支那架運二十運輸機 係老翻c-17   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}